title: 2012-2013 Patch (v1.4.3) for FIFA 11
description:
Contains:
- tool "FIFA 11 Selector"
* easy swith between different databases (squads)
* option OFFLINE (all heads enabled, ...) / ONLINE compatibility
* backup-function: backup your current squads, when you switch squads, and want to continue career later
* Arena options: change Goalkeeper & ball
- updated players (date: 05.07.2013)
* V1: 2012 - 13 squads
* V2: Summer transfers (2013 - 14)
- missing player-skills updated:(skills wich don't exist at fifa 13)
* "developmentstylecode" & "developmenttypecode": development of player at career
* "gkoneonone": how goalkeeper reacts at one on one
* "retirementage": when player stops his career
* "perfconsistencytype": Determines how a player will perform while surrounde
